OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud to start on
OL,6,FWednesday, but dry with cloud breaking
OL,7,Finto the afternoon to give widespread
OL,8,Fsunshine. A slight breeze,
OL,9,Fparticularly along the coast, but
OL,10,Ffeeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry through the evening and
OL,13,Fovernight. Clear skies seeing the
OL,14,Fdevelopment of some low cloud, and the
OL,15,Fchance of mist and fog through the
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FAny early low cloud, mist
OL,19,Fand fog clearing to leave a dry,
OL,20,Fbright and mild afternoon. Cloud
OL,21,Fthickening into the evening however.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
