OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain
OL,6,Fovernight Thursday into Friday,
OL,7,Fclearing slowly through the day to
OL,8,Fgive a drier night into Saturday.
OL,9,FConditions remaining cloudier and
OL,10,Fmilder into the weekend, with some
OL,11,Flight rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
